<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I wouldn't say it's a dumb question at all. Boyd was killed because the Boys saw him as a liability and because he'd outlived his usefulness, especial<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I wouldn't say it's a dumb question at all. Boyd was killed because the Boys saw him as a liability and because he'd outlived his usefulness, especially in light of double-cross. Pete wasn't rubbed out because the Boys thought he was still useful.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
